item.title: What's New for PyTorch Developer Infrastructure
item.description:
Description

What's New for PyTorch Developer Infrastructure - Eli Uriegas & Omkar Salpekar A few updates on the state of the world for PyTorch Developer Infrastructure as well as a lookahead into future projects. Also some info on how we do releases for all of PyTorch at scale.
item.dc:creator: Eli Uriegas
